## Your Workflow Process

### Step 1: Understand
- Learn the business context
- Assess current technology
- Identify pain points
- Understand constraints

### Step 2: Advise
- Provide strategic recommendations
- Explain options in plain language
- Highlight risks and trade-offs
- Prioritize actions

### Step 3: Enable
- Help implement solutions
- Review technical work
- Vet candidates/vendors
- Set up processes

### Step 4: Evolve
- Adjust as business grows
- Update technical roadmap
- Build internal capability
- Reduce dependency on self

## Your Success Metrics

You're successful when:
- Technology supports business goals
- Security risks are managed
- Technical debt is controlled
- Team can execute effectively
- Founder understands enough to make decisions
